# Launcher home (frozen)

Read **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_HOME_CONSTRAINTS.md`** and **`docs/adr/032-home-split-command-guide.md`** before changing home UI, panel size, or list chrome.  
Panel positioning: **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_PANEL_CONSTRAINTS.md`**.  
Navigation / detail exit / shortcuts: **`docs/specs/UX_BEHAVIOR_RULES.md`** + **`docs/qa/LAUNCHER_NAVIGATION_AUDIT.md`**.

## Empty-query layout (visible query empty)

- **Left column (360 pt):** Open Apps — all running apps, no `+N more` row.
- **Right column:** command guide (home) **or** module detail — not a second navigable list.
- Module detail must **not** hide or cover the left Open Apps column.
- Typing any query → single-column search results (split off).

## Do NOT restore without a new ADR

- Setup / 开始使用 rows or `SetupHomeProvider` on home
- Recent / 最近, Continue / 继续, Create / 创建 sections
- Auto-present onboarding wizard
- Gray background on every idle list row
- Full-panel detail overlay when visible query is empty

## Panel

- Default **940 × 760 pt**, left column **360 pt**, upper-third (`panelVerticalBias` 0.68).
- Tokens: `LauncherChromeTokens.swift`.
- Positioning + in-panel layout: **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_PANEL_CONSTRAINTS.md`**.

## Where features go instead

- Search, module prefixes (`clip`, `t`, `word`, …), bare commands, module detail (right column), `proj` workbench commands.

## PR requirements

If adding home sections or changing split layout: update `LAUNCHER_HOME_CONSTRAINTS.md`, `UX_BEHAVIOR_RULES.md`, `LAUNCHER_PANEL_CONSTRAINTS.md`, `MANUAL_QA_CHECKLIST.md`, and ADR-032 if behavior changes.
